  "texts": [
    "MLM creates a mask token that the model will try to guess based on the tokens before and after the masked token.",
    "This allows the pre-training of the model to fuse the sentence's left and right context.",
    "BERT can predict tokens in a pair of sentences separated by a special token ([SEP]).",
    "During BERT model pre-training, at the input, the setence A and sentence B are analogous to creating a paraphrasing sentence pair.",
    "The learned embedding can be added to every token to indicate whether it is from sentence A or from sentence B."
  ],
